    <p><inlineCode parentName="p">{`PoweredBy`}</inlineCode>{` renders the string “Powered by Algolia” with a small logo and link. If you’re using Algolia’s generous free tier, they ask you to acknowledge them in this way below the search results. `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`react-instantsearch-dom`}</inlineCode>{` also provides a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
